      "content": "i get what you're saying but the headache is making it hard to even function right now. i really don't want to wait until my appointment next week to talk to my doctor about it. if i just took a single 200mg advil right now to get through the afternoon, is that actually a huge risk or am i just overthinking it? it's just one pill.",
